パッケージorg.apache.hadoop.registry.client.apiの説明

YARN Registry Client API. This package contains the core API for the YARN registry.
  1. Data types can be found in org.apache.hadoop.registry.client.types
  2. Exceptions are listed in org.apache.hadoop.registry.client.exceptions
  3. Classes to assist use of the registry are in org.apache.hadoop.registry.client.binding
